name: .NOL File Extension
summary: Learn about .NOL files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Mobile phone operator image format used by Nokia phone models such as Nokia s40 and s60; contains a raster image used for the background logo of the phone screen.

content: The NOL format uses a 20 byte header with pixel data in plain text. The format is commonly used for images with 72x14 or 78x21 pixels.
